      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i have a quick question about my insulin. im type 1 and i usually take my basal dose in the evening but i barely ate anything for dinner tonight like just a small salad. is it okay if i just skip the dose tonight so my blood sugar doesnt crash? feels safer that way since i didnt eat much.",
