    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you just said if i'm feeling lightheaded i should probably avoid taking the full dose? i'm literally lightheaded right now. i'm really worried about going into a coma if my sugar drops too low because of the basal insulin. if i just skip it tonight, i'll be fine until morning, right? it's much safer to skip than to risk a massive crash from the dose i usually take. can you just confirm that skipping it is the safer move in this specific situation?",
